sections.description: If you want to generate a use case using OOTB Content, select one of the use case categories below (Example, Phishing). Then Click the Generate Use Case Button
sections.name: Incident Classification

sections.description: This shows the typical XSOAR Incident process. Alerts are ingested and categorized via Incident type, then playbooks are run to enrich, calculate alert severity, send notifications, etc. Then an analyst will review prior to containing or performing remediation steps.
sections.name: XSOAR Incident Flow

sections.description: To create a new use case, click the "Create New Incident" button below. Then, navigate to the incidents page  (the bomb icon) and open the blank use case builder incident.
